        {
            "title": "藥明康德發盈喜 料2025年歸母淨利按年升102.65%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">藥明康德(02357)發盈喜，預期2025年度實現歸屬公司股東淨利潤，約達191.51億元(人民幣．下同)，按年增長102.65%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"藥明康德官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/02359Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"藥明康德官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/02359Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">藥明康德官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上述利潤包括了出售聯營公司部份股權，以及剝離部份業務所獲投資收益。若撇除這類項目，2025年度扣除非經常性損益的歸屬公司東淨利潤，約為132.41億元，按年增長32.56%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">若按非國際財務報告準則，該公司2025年歸屬公司股東的經調整淨利潤約149.57億元，按年升41.33%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期內實現營業收入約454.56億元，按年增長約15.84%，其中持續經營業務收入增長約21.40%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15576382-%e8%97%a5%e6%98%8e%e5%ba%b7%e5%be%b7%e7%99%bc%e7%9b%88%e5%96%9c-%e6%96%992025%e5%b9%b4%e6%ad%b8%e6%af%8d%e6%b7%a8%e5%88%a9%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%87102-65",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250403_FI_source-web_02359-3-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-12 17:00:40",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "明掛牌兩新股暗盤中段齊造好 紅星冷鏈暫漲約50% 兆易創新亦升逾30%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">明天再有兩隻新股登場，今午暗盤中段暫以紅星冷鏈(01641)表現領先，較招股價高約50%，兆易創新(03986)暗盤暫也高招股價逾37%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"兆易創新招股書封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/03986.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"兆易創新招股書封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/03986.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">兆易創新招股書封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">截至下午約4時43分，輝立交易平台顯示紅星冷鏈暗盤報18.9元，較招股價高逾54%；富途交易平台顯示的暗盤則為19.68元，較招股價更高出逾60%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：紅星冷鏈官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20251229_FI_source-web_HNHXLL.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：紅星冷鏈官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20251229_FI_source-web_HNHXLL.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：紅星冷鏈官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">兆易創新在輝立交易平台的暗盤價暫為221.8元，高招股價39.79%；富途交易平台的暗盤價222元，則較招股價高約37%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15576332-%e6%98%8e%e6%8e%9b%e7%89%8c%e5%85%a9%e6%96%b0%e8%82%a1%e6%9a%97%e7%9b%a4%e4%b8%ad%e6%ae%b5%e9%bd%8a%e9%80%a0%e5%a5%bd-%e7%b4%85%e6%98%9f%e5%86%b7%e9%8f%88%e6%9a%ab%e6%bc%b2%e7%b4%8450-%e5%85%86",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250203_FI_source-web_00388-5.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-12 16:50:28",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
