        {
            "title": "全日收市︱午後再上 恒指升376點報26608點 科股多個領域皆揚升 阿里健康突圍成藍籌最強",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地A股價量齊升，港股午後同樣乘勢再上，科股中多個領域均受捧，最後由醫療解決方案平台阿里健康(00241)後來居上成表現最佳藍籌。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"阿里健康官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/00241.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"阿里健康官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/00241.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">阿里健康官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數跟隨外圍高開145點後，初段一度輕微調整，但低位26187點時也僅跌44點，開市約10分鐘後便回復升市，於上午約10時半過後開始發力，展開一浪高於一浪的升軌，早市後段升幅已擴大至逾200點，午市中段升幅進一步提升至逾300點，最後以全日高位收市。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指收報26608點，升276點或1.44%。恒生科技指數全日顯著跑贏大市，收漲176點或3.1%，報5863點；國企指數升171點或1.9%，報9220點。主板成交增至3062.23億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15576207-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e5%86%8d%e4%b8%8a-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%87376%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b126608%e9%bb%9e-%e7%a7%91%e8%82%a1%e5%a4%9a%e5%80%8b%e9%a0%98%e5%9f%9f",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-5.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-12 16:15:38",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "有代理分析樓市小陽春已經出現",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">踏入新一年，本港樓市氣氛持續回暖，綜合市場統計，過去兩日市場共錄得超過310宗一手成交，為近8個月以來最旺的周末。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240524_CR_source_web_Landscape_01.jpeg.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240524_CR_source_web_Landscape_01.jpeg.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新地西沙住宅項目周六開賣213伙價單單位，即日全數沽清。發展商加推兩張價單，合共211伙。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中原地產住宅部總裁陳永傑指出，去年樓價累計升4.7%，年初整體市場氣氛樂觀，市場認為樓市進入升浪，相信「小陽春」已經出現。他估計，今個月一手成交有望突破兩千宗。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">陳永傑又指，過去11年辣招打擊二手市場，現已全面鬆綁，有助買家入市，銀行承造按揭貸款亦較積極。至於二手業主憧憬未來樓市進一步造好，議價空間明顯收窄，現時二手放盤叫價普遍升5%至8%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15575631-%e6%9c%89%e4%bb%a3%e7%90%86%e5%88%86%e6%9e%90%e6%a8%93%e5%b8%82%e5%b0%8f%e9%99%bd%e6%98%a5%e5%b7%b2%e7%b6%93%e5%87%ba%e7%8f%be-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240820_FI_source_licensed_HKProperty_shutterstock_704-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-12 15:25:32",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        }
    ]
}